      "act": "THE EXAMPLE",
      "estimated_duration_s": 12,
      "narration_text": "For hydrogen two-p decaying to one-s by electric-dipole emission, the standard calculation gives a rate near six point three times ten to the eighth per second: a lifetime about one point six nanoseconds.",
