      "act": "LIMITS",
      "estimated_duration_s": 12,
      "narration_text": "The exponential is not exact at all times. Survival begins quadratically at ultrashort times, can show memory or recurrences in structured or finite reservoirs, and develops nonexponential tails at very long times.",
